Key ambitions

• Next level Robust Eco Design for 100% of our relevant product families by 20301

• Waste-to-landfill reduction of 50% by 2025, and towards zero landfill by 20301

• Improve energy efficiency of our sites by 10% until 20301

• Managing water efficiently at own and suppliers’ facilities and providing solutions for customers to handle water and wastewater more efficiently

